constructor(tuple(uint256 expirationTimestamp, uint256 withdrawalLiveness, address collateralAddress, address tokenAddress, address finderAddress, address timerAddress, address financialProductLibraryAddress, bytes32 priceFeedIdentifier, tuple(uint256 rawValue) minSponsorTokens, uint256 liquidationLiveness, tuple(uint256 rawValue) collateralRequirement, tuple(uint256 rawValue) disputeBondPercentage, tuple(uint256 rawValue) sponsorDisputeRewardPercentage, tuple(uint256 rawValue) disputerDisputeRewardPercentage) params)
event Deposit(address indexed sponsor, uint256 indexed collateralAmount)
event DisputeSettled(address indexed caller, address indexed sponsor, address indexed liquidator, address disputer, uint256 liquidationId, bool disputeSucceeded)
event EmergencyShutdown(address indexed caller, uint256 originalExpirationTimestamp, uint256 shutdownTimestamp)

event LiquidationCreated(address indexed sponsor, address indexed liquidator, uint256 indexed liquidationId, uint256 tokensOutstanding, uint256 lockedCollateral, uint256 liquidatedCollateral, uint256 liquidationTime)
event LiquidationDisputed(address indexed sponsor, address indexed liquidator, address indexed disputer, uint256 liquidationId, uint256 disputeBondAmount)
event LiquidationWithdrawn(address indexed caller, uint256 paidToLiquidator, uint256 paidToDisputer, uint256 paidToSponsor, uint8 indexed liquidationStatus, uint256 settlementPrice)
event PositionCreated(address indexed sponsor, uint256 indexed collateralAmount, uint256 indexed tokenAmount)
event Redeem(address indexed sponsor, uint256 indexed collateralAmount, uint256 indexed tokenAmount)
event RegularFeesPaid(uint256 indexed regularFee, uint256 indexed lateFee)
event Repay(address indexed sponsor, uint256 indexed numTokensRepaid, uint256 indexed newTokenCount)
event RequestTransferPositionExecuted(address indexed oldSponsor, address indexed newSponsor)
event RequestWithdrawal(address indexed sponsor, uint256 indexed collateralAmount)
event RequestWithdrawalCanceled(address indexed sponsor, uint256 indexed collateralAmount)
event RequestWithdrawalExecuted(address indexed sponsor, uint256 indexed collateralAmount)
event SettleExpiredPosition(address indexed caller, uint256 indexed collateralReturned, uint256 indexed tokensBurned)
event Withdrawal(address indexed sponsor, uint256 indexed collateralAmount)
function create(tuple(uint256 rawValue) collateralAmount, tuple(uint256 rawValue) numTokens)

function createLiquidation(address sponsor, tuple(uint256 rawValue) minCollateralPerToken, tuple(uint256 rawValue) maxCollateralPerToken, tuple(uint256 rawValue) maxTokensToLiquidate, uint256 deadline) returns (uint256 liquidationId, tuple(uint256 rawValue) tokensLiquidated, tuple(uint256 rawValue) finalFeeBond)
function depositTo(address sponsor, tuple(uint256 rawValue) collateralAmount)
function dispute(uint256 liquidationId, address sponsor) returns (tuple(uint256 rawValue) totalPaid)
function getCollateral(address sponsor) view returns (tuple(uint256 rawValue))

function getLiquidations(address sponsor) view returns (tuple(address sponsor, address liquidator, uint8 state, uint256 liquidationTime, tuple(uint256 rawValue) tokensOutstanding, tuple(uint256 rawValue) lockedCollateral, tuple(uint256 rawValue) liquidatedCollateral, tuple(uint256 rawValue) rawUnitCollateral, address disputer, tuple(uint256 rawValue) settlementPrice, tuple(uint256 rawValue) finalFee)[] liquidationData)
function getOutstandingRegularFees(uint256 time) view returns (tuple(uint256 rawValue) regularFee, tuple(uint256 rawValue) latePenalty, tuple(uint256 rawValue) totalPaid)

function liquidations(address, uint256) view returns (address sponsor, address liquidator, uint8 state, uint256 liquidationTime, tuple(uint256 rawValue) tokensOutstanding, tuple(uint256 rawValue) lockedCollateral, tuple(uint256 rawValue) liquidatedCollateral, tuple(uint256 rawValue) rawUnitCollateral, address disputer, tuple(uint256 rawValue) settlementPrice, tuple(uint256 rawValue) finalFee)

function positions(address) view returns (tuple(uint256 rawValue) tokensOutstanding, uint256 withdrawalRequestPassTimestamp, tuple(uint256 rawValue) withdrawalRequestAmount, tuple(uint256 rawValue) rawCollateral, uint256 transferPositionRequestPassTimestamp)
function redeem(tuple(uint256 rawValue) numTokens) returns (tuple(uint256 rawValue) amountWithdrawn)
function transformCollateralRequirement(tuple(uint256 rawValue) price) view returns (tuple(uint256 rawValue))
function transformPrice(tuple(uint256 rawValue) price, uint256 requestTime) view returns (tuple(uint256 rawValue))
function withdraw(tuple(uint256 rawValue) collateralAmount) returns (tuple(uint256 rawValue) amountWithdrawn)

function withdrawLiquidation(uint256 liquidationId, address sponsor) returns (tuple(tuple(uint256 rawValue) payToSponsor, tuple(uint256 rawValue) payToLiquidator, tuple(uint256 rawValue) payToDisputer, tuple(uint256 rawValue) paidToSponsor, tuple(uint256 rawValue) paidToLiquidator, tuple(uint256 rawValue) paidToDisputer))
